title: Firefox Jun2016 portable (runs of USB drive sep from windows
description:
Firefox Jun2016 portable (runs of USB drive and dont install anything in windows)

I came across this a few months ago. looked handy and could try out the
latest build without lossing the exist installed windows one


the exe is a unpacker.. will unzip the files to location you want
a folder or USB drive

then just run the firefoxportable.exe in the unzipped folder

can install other things like plugins

this ver dont download to install and nothing to profile folders

can have own bookmarks and browser with you at all times with fav plugins

and use on mates computer without affecting their copy



can work with existing installed windows versions but I dont think they can run at the same time
